Package: reflex
Version: 0.2.0+git20181022.3df204f-1
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Kyle Robbertze <krobbertze@gmail.com>
Installed-Size: 1930
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.3.2)
Built-Using: golang-1.10 (= 1.10.4-2), golang-fsnotify (= 1.4.7-2), golang-github-kballard-go-shellquote (= 0.0~git20150810.0.d8ec1a6-2), golang-github-ogier-pflag (= 0.0~git20160129.0.45c278a-3), golang-golang-x-sys (= 0.0~git20180510.7dfd129-1), golang-pty (= 1.1.2-1)
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/cespare/reflex
Description: Run a command when files change
 Reflex is a small tool to watch a directory and rerun a command
 when certain files change. It's great for automatically running
 compile/lint/test tasks and for reloading your application when the
 code changes.
